Icon

Use an icon to add an extra visual element to a label.

Installation 

                  
                    npm i @govflanders/vl-ui-icon

or 

                  
                    yarn add @govflanders/vl-ui-icon

Usage

Import SASS 

                  
                  @import "vl-ui-icon/src/scss/icon";

Make sure your sass --include-path includes node_modules/@govflanders/.

HTML markup 

      <span class="vl-icon vl-vi vl-vi-<icon-name>" aria-hidden="true"></span>

To use an icon, replace <icon-name> with one of the icon names below.

Variants

Only child

The size of the icon is defined by the parent. If the icon is an only child, it won't append any margin left or right.

      
        <p class=""><span class="vl-icon vl-vi vl-vi-calendar" aria-hidden="true"></span></p>

Icon appended before any other element

Use the before modifier to add proper spacing between the icon and the following content. If the icon is the first child, spacing will be appended as well.

Integer posuere erat a ante venenatis dapibus posuere velit aliquet.

      
        <p class="vl-icon-wrapper"><span class="vl-icon vl-icon--before vl-vi vl-vi-calendar" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Integer posuere erat a ante venenatis dapibus posuere velit aliquet.</span></p>

Icon appended after any other element

Use the after modifier to add proper spacing between the icon and the previous content. If the icon is the last child, spacing will be appended as well.

Integer posuere erat a ante venenatis dapibus posuere velit aliquet.

      
        <p class="vl-icon-wrapper"><span>Integer posuere erat a ante venenatis dapibus posuere velit aliquet.</span><span class="vl-icon vl-icon--after vl-vi vl-vi-nav-right" aria-hidden="true"></span></p>

Small size

Use the small modifier to make the icon 80% in size compared to it's parent.

      
        <p class=""><span class="vl-icon vl-icon--small vl-vi vl-vi-calendar" aria-hidden="true"></span></p>

Large size

Use the large modifier to make the icon 120% in size compared to it's parent.

      
        <p class=""><span class="vl-icon vl-icon--large vl-vi vl-vi-chat-help" aria-hidden="true"></span></p>

Light

Use the light modifier to give the icon a light color.

      
        <p class="vl-icon-wrapper"><span class="vl-icon vl-icon--light vl-vi vl-vi-chat-help" aria-hidden="true"></span></p>

Icon wrapper

Use vl-icon-wrapper on the parent of the icon to vertically align all children.

My icon is aligned neatly in the middle

      
        <p class="vl-icon-wrapper"><span class="vl-icon vl-icon--before vl-vi vl-vi-chat-help" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>My icon is aligned neatly in the middle</span></p>
